                "reaction": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " A deuterium gas target fitted with 5 um Mo",
                "entrance foil and 1 mm Pt beams top is bombarded with a",
                "deuteron beam of the appropriate energy. The gas cell",
                "has a total length of 3.7 cm and a diameter of 1 cm,",
                "and is typically pressurized to 1.2 atm."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "IOCH"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The detection system consisted of a stack of",
                "ionisation gas cells based on the Micromegas Microbulk",
                "technology for the detection of the fission fragments,",
                "each one containing one actinide target, the backing",
                "of which served as the detector drift electrode."
              ]
            }
          ],
